法規內容.條文內容:
These Regulations shall be applied to the following visa documents:
1.Import/Export Permits;
2.Application for Optical Disk Manufacturing Implement Export/Import Declarations;
3.Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora (CITES) Permits;
4.Export Permits for Strategic High-Tech Commodities;
5.International Import Certificates of Strategic High-Tech Commodities;
6.Written Assurance Certificates of Strategic High-Tech Commodities Import;
7.End-Use Certificate for Chemicals of the Chemical Weapons Convention;
8.Other visa documents that must be applied for electronically, as publicly announced by BOFT.

Applicants applying for visa documents shall do so by electronic means, unless either of the following two situations exists, in which case they shall apply by means of writing:
1.The BOFT computer system breaks down;
2.Application is made for replacement of lost visa documents.
